title: Complete the Square
text: Group and factor: $$4\left(x^2+6x\right)$$ + $$\operatorname{16}\left(y^2-8y\right)$$ $$=$$ $$-228$$. Then complete the square.

title: Divide to Get Standard Form
text: After completing the square: $$\frac{\left(x+3\right)^2}{25}$$ + $$\frac{\left(y-4\right)^2}{4}$$ $$=$$ $$1$$. Identify a $$=$$ $$5$$, $$b$$ $$=$$ $$2$$.
